<div class="pair-comparison-block">
    {% if comparison.summary is defined %}
    <p class="pair-comparison__summary">{{ comparison.summary }}</p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if comparison.overall_agreement is defined %}
    <div class="pair-comparison__agreement">
        <div class="agreement-bar">
            <div class="agreement-fill" style="width: {{ comparison.overall_agreement }}%"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="agreement-label">Согласованность: {{ comparison.overall_agreement }}%</span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <table class="pair-comparison__table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th class="col-item">Пункт</th>
                <th class="col-score">Вы</th>
                <th class="col-score">Партнёр</th>
                <th class="col-diff">Разница</th>
                <th class="col-gap">Ваш perception gap</th>
                <th class="col-gap">Партнёр perception gap</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for item in comparison.items %}
            <tr class="row-diff-{{ item.difference|abs }}">
                <td class="col-item">
                    <span class="item-domain">{{ item.domain }}</span>
                    <span class="item-text">{{ item.text }}</span>
                </td>
                <td class="col-score">{{ item.p1_self ?? '—' }}</td>
                <td class="col-score">{{ item.p2_self ?? '—' }}</td>
                <td class="col-diff {{ item.difference == 0 ? 'diff-match' : 'diff-mismatch' }}">
                    {% if item.difference is not null %}
                        {% if item.difference > 0 %}+{{ item.difference }}{% else %}{{ item.difference }}{% endif %}
                    {% else %}—{% endif %}
                </td>
                <td class="col-gap {{ item.p1_accuracy is not null and item.p1_accuracy|abs >= 2 ? 'gap-large' : '' }}">
                    {% if item.p1_accuracy is not null %}
                        {% if item.p1_accuracy > 0 %}+{{ item.p1_accuracy }}{% else %}{{ item.p1_accuracy }}{% endif %}
                    {% else %}—{% endif %}
                </td>
                <td class="col-gap {{ item.p2_accuracy is not null and item.p2_accuracy|abs >= 2 ? 'gap-large' : '' }}">
                    {% if item.p2_accuracy is not null %}
                        {% if item.p2_accuracy > 0 %}+{{ item.p2_accuracy }}{% else %}{{ item.p2_accuracy }}{% endif %}
                    {% else %}—{% endif %}
                </td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="pair-comparison__legend">
        <p><strong>Разница</strong> — расхождение между вашей оценкой и оценкой партнёра (0 = полное совпадение).</p>
        <p><strong>Perception gap</strong> — насколько вы (или партнёр) угадали ответ другого. Отрицательный = недооценили, положительный = переоценили.</p>
    </div>
</div>
